1333年","1250":"1250年","1272":"1272年",",Scotland.":"英國蘇格蘭","lifeSummary":"Baron Robert Boyd是Lord Robert V Boyd的兒子，於大約1272年出生在英國蘇格蘭。他至少有1個兒子。他去世於大約1333年享年63歲。"},"zh-hans":{"about 1272–ABT 1333":"大约1272年–大约1333年","1272–1333":"1272年–1333年","1299–1365":"1299年–1365年","1250–Male":"1250年–殁","about 1272":"大约1272年","1333":"1333年","1365":"1365年","1299":"1299年","ABT 1333":"大约1333年","1250":"1250年","1272":"1272年",",Scotland.":"英国苏格兰","lifeSummary":"Baron Robert Boyd是Lord Robert V Boyd的儿子，于大约1272年出生在英国苏格兰。他至少有1个儿子。他去世于大约1333年享年63岁。"},"hr":{"about 1272–ABT 1333":"oko 1272.–oko 1333.","1272–1333":"1272–1333","1299–1365":"1299–1365","1250–Male":"1250–preminuo","about 1272":"oko 1272.","1333":"1333","1365":"1365","1299":"1299","ABT 1333":"oko 1333.","1250":"1250","1272":"1272",",Scotland.":"Škotska, United Kingdom"},"cs":{"about 1272–ABT 1333":"okolo 1272–okolo 1333","1272–1333":"1272–1333","1299–1365":"1299–1365","1250–Male":"1250–Zesnulý","about 1272":"okolo 1272","1333":"1333","1365":"1365","1299":"1299","ABT 1333":"okolo 1333","1250":"1250","1272":"1272",",Scotland.":"Skotsko, United Kingdom"},"da":{"about 1272–ABT 1333":"omkring 1272–omkring 1333","1272–1333":"1272–1333","1299–1365":"1299–1365","1250–Male":"1250–Afdød","about 1272":"omkring 1272","1333":"1333","1365":"1365","1299":"1299","ABT 1333":"omkring 1333","1250":"1250","1272":"1272",",Scotland.":"Skotland, United Kingdom"},"nl":{"about 1272–ABT 1333":"circa 1272–circa 1333","1272–1333":"1272–1333","1299–1365":"1299–1365","1250–Male":"1250–Overleden","about 1272":"circa 1272","1333":"1333","1365":"1365","1299":"1299","ABT 1333":"circa 1333","1250":"1250","1272":"1272",",Scotland.":"Schotland, Verenigd Koninkrijk"},"en":{"about 1272–ABT 1333":"about 1272–about 1333","1272–1333":"1272–1333","1299–1365":"1299–1365","1250–Male":"1250–Deceased","about 1272":"about 1272","1333":"1333","1365":"1365","1299":"1299","ABT 1333":"about 1333","1250":"1250","1272":"1272",",Scotland.":"Scotland, United Kingdom","nameMeanings":[{"name":"Boyd","type":"LAST","attribution":"Dictionary of American Family Names © Patrick Hanks 2003, 2006.","meanings":["Scottish: habitational name from the island of Bute in the Firth of Clyde, from <i>Bòid</i> (genitive case of <i>Bòd</i>, the Gaelic name of the island of Bute) or <i>Bòideach</i>, denoting a person from Bute. Alternatively, the name may denote descendants of a <i>Gilla filius Boed</i>, who appears in reference to Glasgow Cathedral in the early 12th century, perhaps from the Gaelic personal name <i>Boite</i>, of uncertain origin.","Scottish and Irish: from the Gaelic epithet <i>buidhe</i> ‘yellow(-haired)’. Compare   Bowie  .","Manx: from <b>Mac Gille Buidhe</b> ‘son of the yellow-haired lad’ (compare 2 above)."],"variants":[{"name":"Bowie","meanings":["Scottish: from Gaelic <i>buidhe</i> ‘yellow’, i.e. ‘yellow-haired’, pronounced as two syllables. The equivalent term in Ireland is <i>buí</i>, often Anglicized as <i>boy</i>. The surname may also be a shortened form of   Gilboy  .","Irish: Anglicized form of <b>Ó Buadhaigh</b> (see   Bogue  )."]},{"name":"Boyde","meanings":["Scottish (Glasgow): variant of   Boyd  ."]}]},{"name":"Robert","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["One of the many French names of Germanic origin that were introduced into Britain by the Normans; it has since remained in continuous use. It is derived from the nearly synonymous elements <i>hrōd</i> ‘fame’ + <i>berht</i> ‘bright, famous’, and had a native Old English predecessor of similar form (<i>Hreodbeorht</i>), which was supplanted by the Norman name. Two dukes of Normandy in the 11th century bore the name: the father of  William the Conqueror  (sometimes identified with the legendary Robert the Devil), and his eldest son. It was borne also by three kings of Scotland, notably  Robert the Bruce  (  1274–1329 ), who freed Scotland from English domination. The altered short form <i>Bob</i> is very common, but <i>Hob</i> and <i>Dob</i>, which were common in the Middle Ages and gave rise to surnames, are extinct.  See also  Rupert ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Baron Robert Boyd was born about 1272, in Scotland, United Kingdom as the son of Lord Robert V Boyd. He had at least 1 son. He died about 1333, at the age of 63."},"et":{"about 1272–ABT 1333":"umbes 1272–umbes 1333","1272–1333":"1272–1333","1299–1365":"1299–1365","1250–Male":"1250–Surnud","about 1272":"umbes 1272","1333":"1333","1365":"1365","1299":"1299","ABT 1333":"umbes 1333","1250":"1250","1272":"1272",",Scotland.":"Šotimaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"about 1272–ABT 1333":"noin 1272–noin 1333","1272–1333":"1272–1333","1299–1365":"1299–1365","1250–Male":"1250–Kuollut","about 1272":"noin 1272","1333":"1333","1365":"1365","1299":"1299","ABT 1333":"noin 1333","1250":"1250","1272":"1272",",Scotland.":"Skotlanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"about 1272–ABT 1333":"environ 1272–environ 1333","1272–1333":"1272–1333","1299–1365":"1299–1365","1250–Male":"1250–Décédé","about 1272":"environ 1272","1333":"1333","1365":"1365","1299":"1299","ABT 1333":"environ 1333","1250":"1250","1272":"1272",",Scotland.":"Écosse, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Baron Robert Boyd est né environ 1272, à Écosse, Royaume-Uni, fils de Lord Robert V Boyd. Il a eu au moins 1 fils. Il est décédé environ 1333, à l’âge de 63 ans."},"de":{"about 1272–ABT 1333":"um 1272–um 1333","1272–1333":"1272–1333","1299–1365":"1299–1365","1250–Male":"1250–Verstorben","about 1272":"um 1272","1333":"1333","1365":"1365","1299":"1299","ABT 1333":"um 1333","1250":"1250","1272":"1272",",Scotland.":"Schottland, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Baron Robert Boyd wurde um 1272 in Schottland, United Kingdom, als Sohn von Lord Robert V Boyd geboren. Er hatte mindestens 1 Sohn. Er starb um 1333 im Alter von 63 Jahren."},"ht":{"about 1272–ABT 1333":"about 1272–about 1333","1272–1333":"1272–1333","1299–1365":"1299–1365","1250–Male":"1250–Desede","about 1272":"about 1272"